### 1. Register admin user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@jewelcart.com",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@jewelcart.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 3. Protected endpoint WITHOUT token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/vendors

### 4. Protected endpoint WITH token (paste token from step 2)
